{
  "description": "The image depicts a weathered, grey wooden plank lying horizontally across the top of the frame. The wood shows clear signs of age and exposure, with visible grain, cracks, and patches of greenish-yellow lichen or moss. A prominent knot is visible in the wood, adding to its rustic character. Below the plank is a dense field of tall, green grasses and wildflowers, softly blurred to create a shallow depth of field. The grasses are various shades of green, with some flowering stalks bearing seed heads. The lighting is soft and diffused, creating a natural and peaceful atmosphere. The composition emphasizes the contrast between the solid, aged wood and the vibrant, growing vegetation.",
